nodes.text: A quarantine inspector was tasked with carefully checking astrocultural freight for a travel agency's customs. By the year 4.3 ABY,the quarantine inspectors for the Star Tours travel agency's Tomorrowland Starport were two PanaRobos, P-6 and S-4. They worked in the Quarantine Section of the starport's Baggage Claim, under the supervision of an R2 unit.
